author: nowaynas
title: nowaynas
text: I love having the VIP membership! I used to hate spending money on workout clothes because they can be so pricey, but with these deals I finally feel like it's worth it. i have totally revamped my fitness wardrobe and I get super excited to see what is available each month. I love the no commitment option to opt out of the auto enrollment, but I usually can't say no once I see what's available.
